»» Description:

		This plugin allows you to manage folders under the "git".
		Command applies to all folders IN THE FOLDER "barrel".

		Full path to "barrel" should be: ~/.pentadactyl/plugins/barrel


»» Dependences:
		You must have _lib-app.js

»» Examples:

		For example you can fetch changes for all plugins at once, using command:
		+-------------------------------------------------+
		| :octopus fetch <remoate-name>                   |
		+-------------------------------------------------+

		Or check status plugins:
		+-----------------------------------+
		| :octopus status                   |
		+-----------------------------------+

To execute command for one directory, you must define optoins -directory or -D 
		+-----------------------------------+
		| :octopus -D octopus status        |
		+-----------------------------------+
